        <p class="metadata">Posted by Mickael Perraud (mikaelkael) on 2009-02-03T07:10:09.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>There is a lazy loading of metadata. Before calling, $this-&gt;_cols you need to populate by $this-&gt;_setupMetadata().</p>

<p>The better way is to call $this-&gt;info(self::COLS) that does it for you.</p>

